              <td>{{ .Name }}</td>
          </tr>
        {{ end}}
      </table>

      </section>
    </div>

    <div class="clearfix"></div>
    <div class="deposit-history">
      <h1> Deposit History </h1>

      <section class="deposit-history-table">
      <table class="table table-striped transactions">
          <thead>
              <tr>
                  <th class="date"> Date</th>
                  <th class="description"> Description</th>
                  <th class="account-name"> Account Name</th>
                  <th class="account-amount"> Amount</th>
                  <th class="largest-deposit"> Largest Deposit</th>
              </tr>
          </thead>
          {{ range .DepositHistory }}
          <tr>
              <td>{{ .Date.Format "2006-01-02" }}</td>
              <td>{{ .Description }}</td>
              <td>{{ .AccountName }}</td>
              <td>{{ .Amount }}</td>
              <td>{{ if .LargeDeposit }} Yes {{ else }} No {{ end }}</td>
          </tr>
        {{ end}}
      </table>

      </section>
    </div>

    <div class="clearfix"></div>
    <div class="verification-of-assets">
      <h1> Verification Of Assets </h1>

      <section class="verification-of-assets-table">
      <table class="table table-striped assets">
          <thead>
              <tr>
                  <th class="archIn"> AchIn</th>
                  <th class="archOut"> AchOut</th>
                  <th class="assets-requested"> Asset Requested</th>
                  <th class="assets-returned"> Asset Returned</th>
                  <th class="direct-deposit"> Direct Deposit</th>
                  <th class="linked"> Linked</th>
              </tr>
          </thead>
          {{ range .VerificationOfAssets }}
          <tr>
              <td>{{ if .AchIn }} Yes {{ else }} No {{ end }}</td>
              <td>{{ if .AchOut }} Yes {{ else }} No {{ end }}</td>
              <td>{{ .AssetRequested }}</td>
              <td>{{ .AssetReturned }}</td>
              <td>{{ if .DirectDeposit }} Yes {{ else }} No {{ end }}</td>
              <td>{{ if .Linked }} Yes {{ else }} No {{ end }}</td>
          </tr>
        {{ end}}
      </table>

      </section>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
